For accommodation, I'm flexible but would prefer something clean and safe, maybe downtown or in a area that's walkable to restaurants and attractions. I don't have any hotel loyalty programs.

As for food, I don't have any dietary restrictions and I'm pretty adventurous when it comes to trying new things. Definitely want to experience some authentic Wisconsin cuisine!"
